<messaging:emailTemplate subject="A new product {!relatedTo.ASI_CN_NPL_Product_Name_English__c} TP per case (with currency) is waiting for your approval. Ref:{!relatedTo.Id}" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_CN_NPL_NPL_Request__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody >Dear FINANCE Uers,<br/><br/><apex:variable rendered="{!relatedTo.ASI_NPL_ETA_Domestic__c != null}" value="1" var="1">Domestic:For your information, a new product {!relatedTo.ASI_CN_NPL_Product_Name_English__c}'s TP per case (with currency) information is available now, please kindly approve it <b>before ETA</b>(<apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy-MM-dd}"><apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_NPL_ETA_Domestic__c}"/></apex:outputText> ). <br/></apex:variable><apex:variable rendered="{!relatedTo.ASI_NPL_ETA__c != null}" value="1" var="1">Macau and Mongolia:For your information, a new product {!relatedTo.ASI_CN_NPL_Product_Name_English__c}'s TP per case (with currency) information is available now, please kindly approve it <b>before ETA</b>(<apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy-MM-dd}"><apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_NPL_ETA__c}"/></apex:outputText> ). <br/></apex:variable>You could view the detail at <a href="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND(".com/",$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!relatedto.id}">{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND(".com/",$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!relatedto.id}</a> or by reply this email with keywords - <apex:outputText value=" APPROVE, APPROVED, YES, REJECT, REJECTED, NO." style="color:red;font-weight:bold; "/><br/></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>